summary: An Ordinance approving the assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 1697, for the improvement of Lane Street, from Eighteenth Avenue South to Rainier Avenue, and Sixteenth Avenue South, from Weller Street to Lane Street, all in the City of Seattle, by grading and curbing the same under Ordinance No. 17945 and assessing the amounts thereof against each parcel and lot of land and part thereof shown in said roll, and providing for the collection thereof.
